  <div id="text-content_E2D65F20-1E1B-0135-BF26-22000B5A851D" class="text-block-content">
    <p>If you allow students to like announcements, you can like announcement replies in your course. To view the Like icon on announcements, you must <a href="/t5/Instructor-Guide/How-do-I-allow-students-to-like-replies-in-a-course-announcement/ta-p/1220" target="_blank">allow users to like replies in a course announcement</a>.</p>
<p>If the steps in this lesson do not match what is displayed in your course, learn how to <a href="/t5/Instructor-Guide/How-do-I-like-a-reply-in-a-course-announcement-in-Announcements/ta-p/478618" target="_blank">like a reply to an announcement in the Announcements Redesign interface</a>.</p>
  </div>
</div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="open_announcements" data-step-uuid="0ec339ac-1f5e-4e78-809c-96c811a1e045">
    <h2 id="open_announcements" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Open Announcements</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/002/740/456/original/2f0f22be-6f46-4681-bdc5-3806229a73bf.png" srcset="" alt="Open Announcements" height="267" width="179">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_E2D82BA0-1E1B-0135-BF28-22000B5A851D" class="text-block-content">
    <p>In Course Navigation, click the <strong>Announcements</strong> link.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="open_announcement" data-step-uuid="789aac36-dde7-4aae-ac86-07dc73c34410">
    <h2 id="open_announcement" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Open Announcement</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <a href="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/001/487/913/original/1d68cd1d-ef9e-4753-a620-e5e3fd0d88bc.png" class="screensteps-image-zoom" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer">
        <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/001/487/913/medium/1d68cd1d-ef9e-4753-a620-e5e3fd0d88bc.png" srcset="" alt="Open Announcement" height="242" width="855">
      </a>
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_E2D88580-1E1B-0135-BF2A-22000B5A851D" class="text-block-content">
    <p>Click the name of the announcement.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="like_announcement_reply" data-step-uuid="cc957921-dc46-4b9e-9473-081c0fb5fde2">
    <h2 id="like_announcement_reply" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Like Announcement Reply</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/001/365/741/original/87379be3-64c4-4094-a62d-00b000c75615.png" srcset="" alt="Like Announcement Reply" height="316" width="638">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_E2D8D530-1E1B-0135-BF2C-22000B5A851D" class="text-block-content">
    <p>Locate the reply and click the <strong>Like </strong>icon.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
        <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-2" id="view_liked_reply" data-step-uuid="fe5cb2b8-513e-4628-b181-1c2557092738">
    <h3 id="view_liked_reply" class="step-title screensteps-heading">View Liked Reply</h3>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/001/365/739/original/7d3f7c78-48e2-4fad-a2c4-ddc51d370fed.png" srcset="" alt="View Liked Reply" height="322" width="650">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_E2D91860-1E1B-0135-BF2E-22000B5A851D" class="text-block-content">
    <p>The Like icon will be highlighted, indicating you have liked the reply. </p>
<p>When a reply is liked, the Like icon will also display the total number of likes for all users in the announcement.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>
 
  </div>
					
				
			
			
			
				
			
			
			
			
			
			
